Class DelegatingProperties

java.lang.Object
  java.util.Dictionary<K,V>

              com.oracle.tools.runtime.java.virtualization.DelegatingProperties
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Cloneable, Map<Object,Object>
public class DelegatingProperties
extends Properties

A DelegatingProperties is a Properties implementation that delegates Properties method calls onto appropriate VirtualizedSystem.getProperties().
